    props: { title: "APY vs APR: What Is the Difference?", categoryName: "DeFi Lending", categorySlug: "defi-lending", readTime: "7 min", intro: "APY and APR are the two most common metrics for expressing DeFi yields, but they represent fundamentally different things. Understanding the difference is essential for accurately comparing investment opportunities and estimating your actual returns. This guide breaks down both metrics with clear examples." },
